pageContext.description: Ribs slightly raised; casting seem visible but not strongly marked. large hole (ancient) under loop.
pageContext.patina: Shuny light green patina, worn off in places where very light dusty green matte surface is exposed.
pageContext.associations: Found in a hole, beneath a stone slab, with about 40-50 others, mostly broken and apparently laid in rows.
